<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: light;
            --ink: #172033;
            --muted: #5f6b7d;
            --line: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.12);
            --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
            --accent: #f25f4c;
            --accent-strong: #c53f2d;
            --accent-soft: rgba(242, 95, 76, 0.14);
            --ok: #1c7c54;
            --warn: #a06100;
            --bg-top: #f6efe7;
            --bg-bottom: #e8eef7;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Avenir Next", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            color: var(--ink);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(242, 95, 76, 0.16), transparent 28rem),
                linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-top), var(--bg-bottom));
        }

        main {
            max-width: 1080px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 20px 64px;
        }

        .hero {
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.08);
        }

        .eyebrow {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            color: var(--accent-strong);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 4.2rem);
            line-height: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        }

        .lede {
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin: 16px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .banner {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .banner.success {
            background: rgba(28, 124, 84, 0.12);
            color: var(--ok);
        }

        .banner.warning {
            background: rgba(160, 97, 0, 0.12);
            color: var(--warn);
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 48px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 140ms ease, background 140ms ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: var(--accent-strong);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .subtle-link {
            color: var(--ink);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 22px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 42px rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.06);
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .card p,
        .card li {
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .stack {
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .urls {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .url-block {
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .url-block strong,
        .status-label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        code {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.08);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: "SFMono-Regular", "Menlo", monospace;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        ul,
        ol {
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .status-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .status-list li {
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        }

        .status-list li.ready {
            border-color: rgba(28, 124, 84, 0.22);
        }

        .status-list li.pending {
            border-color: rgba(160, 97, 0, 0.22);
            background: rgba(255, 246, 230, 0.8);
        }

        .status-value {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .scope-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .scope-list li {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent-soft);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        @media (min-width: 860px) {
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
            }

            .card.full {
                grid-column: 1 / -1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
    <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Slack Slash Command Setup</p>
        <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
        <p class="lede">
            Install the app into your Slack workspace, then use <code>/stamp :emoji:</code> to post
            a larger version of that emoji into the current channel.
        </p>

        {{#if connected}}
            <div class="banner success">
                Slack workspace installation completed successfully. Return to Slack and try
                <code>/stamp :thumbsup:</code>.
            </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if needsPublicBaseUrl}}
            <div class="banner warning">
                <strong>Slack cannot call localhost directly.</strong>
                Set <code>APP_BASE_URL</code> to your public HTTPS tunnel or deployed URL before installing the app.
            </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="actions">
            {{#if addToSlackUrl}}
                <a class="button" href="{{ addToSlackUrl }}">Add to Slack</a>
            {{else}}
                <span class="banner warning">Set <code>SLACK_CLIENT_ID</code> to render the Add to Slack link.</span>
            {{/if}}
            <a class="subtle-link" href="https://api.slack.com/apps">Open Slack App Settings</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
            <h2>Slack Configuration</h2>
            <div class="stack">
                <div class="urls">
                    <div class="url-block">
                        <strong>OAuth redirect URL</strong>
                        <code>{{ oauthRedirectUrl }}</code>
                    </div>
                    <div class="url-block">
                        <strong>Slash command request URL</strong>
                        <code>{{ slashCommandUrl }}</code>
                    </div>
                    <div class="url-block">
                        <strong>Post-auth redirect</strong>
                        <code>{{ authSuccessRedirectUrl }}</code>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <strong class="status-label">Bot scopes</strong>
                    <ul class="scope-list">
                        {{#each botScopes}}
                            <li>{{ this }}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <strong class="status-label">User scopes</strong>
                    {{#if hasUserScopes}}
                        <ul class="scope-list">
                            {{#each userScopes}}
                                <li>{{ this }}</li>
                            {{/each}}
                        </ul>
                    {{else}}
                        <p>No user scopes required.</p>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h2>Environment Status</h2>
            <ul class="status-list">
                {{#each setupChecklist}}
                    <li class="{{#if this.ready}}ready{{else}}pending{{/if}}">
                        <strong class="status-label">{{ this.label }}</strong>
                        <div class="status-value"><code>{{ this.value }}</code></div>
                    </li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card full">
            <h2>Quick Start</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Run <code>cp .env.example .env</code> and fill in your Slack credentials.</li>
                <li>Start PostgreSQL with <code>docker compose up -d postgres</code> or point the app at an existing database.</li>
                <li>Set <code>APP_BASE_URL</code> to your public HTTPS URL if you are testing from localhost.</li>
                <li>Copy the Slack app's signing secret into <code>SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET</code>.</li>
                <li>Create a Slash Command in Slack and set its request URL to <code>{{ slashCommandUrl }}</code>.</li>
                <li>Install the app once for the workspace, then run <code>/stamp :emoji:</code> inside Slack.</li>
            </ol>
        </article>
    </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
